<p>

Four vacancies remain on the House Economic
and Educational Opportunities Committee for the 105th Congress.
Below is a list of committee members to date.  Rep. Bill Goodling
(R-Pa.) will continue as chairman.  A change in the committee's
name has been discussed.  If the name is changed, it will occur
on the first day of the 105th Congress.

