<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Average cost of a hotel room: $80</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<P>
<center>
<a href="/atr/tax-presentation/gunoped.html">next</a> | 2 of 8 | <a href="/atr/tax-presentation/mealoped.html">previous</a><br><FONT SIZE=6><a href="/atr/tax-presentation/payhotel.html">Average cost of a hotel room: $80</a></font><p>
</center>
<p>
<img src="/atr/sept96/bellboy.gif" align="left">

<P>
<blockquote>
<CENTER><U><FONT SIZE=5>Taxes Imposed on Hotels<BR>
</FONT></U></CENTER>
<P>
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=5>Federal Income Taxes</FONT></CENTER>
<P>
