<TITLE>Press Releases</TITLE>


<CENTER><H2>Press Releases</H2></CENTER>
<h5><a href="/townhall/media_services/welcome.html.cgi">[Graphics On]</a></h5>









<BR><HR WIDTH=50%>
<BR>
<BR>Media Services provides the latest press releases from the Citizens of Town Hall.
<P>
</center>
<UL>
<li>Heritage Foundation/<i>Wall Street Journal</i>--<a href="/heritage/news/97index1.html">Only Eight of 150 World Economies Rated "Free" on 1997 "Index of Economic Freedom"</a>. December 15, 1996
<li>Heritage Foundation/<i>Wall Street Journal</i>--<a href="/heritage/news/97index2.html">Foreign Aid Can Impede Economic Growth in Poor Countries,  1997 "Index of Economic Freedom" Shows</a>. December 15, 1996
<li>Heritage Foundation--<a href="/heritage/news/apec96.html">On Eve of Summit, Asian Countries Question U.S. Commitment to Free Trade, Analyst Says</a>. November 19, 1996
<li>Heritage Foundation--<a href="/heritage/news/foia.html">Heritage Calls for Congressional Freedom of Information Act</a>. November 15, 1996
