<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/discovery/networks.html 204.71.237.74 19970108124643 text/html 6390
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 12:47:01 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 08:31:03 GMT
