http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/columnists/otb/AL/alfa0827.html 204.71.237.74 19970108125920 text/html 5254
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 12:59:27 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 27-Aug-96 15:24:08 GMT
