http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/columnists/otb/NV/supr2.html 204.71.237.74 19970108130443 text/html 6900
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 13:04:56 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 26-Sep-96 13:31:08 GMT
Content-length: 6712
