<CENTER><H1>Gary L. Bauer Publications</H1>
</CENTER><HR SIZE=3 WIDTH=50%>
<P>
<img src="/townhall/FRC/images/ohod.gif" align=left hspace=12 vspace=12>
<A NAME = "hope"><I>Our Hopes, Our Dreams</I></a><BR>
Gary Bauer<BR>
Focus on the Family Publishing, (Softback, 166pp.) <BR>
Suggested Donation: $3.99
<P>
What do pro-family Americans really want? What would our platform mean to the tax code, to the schools, to the entertainment industry, to business -- and, above all, to our neighborhoods? <i>Our Hopes, Our Dreams</I>, the new book by Gary L. Bauer, Former Undersecretary of Education and White House domestic policy chief, provides an answer to these and other tough questions.<p>
<i>Our Hopes, Our Dreams</i> gives you a concise, affordable resource that explains the pro-family message.<p>

<center><b>
Purchase this book from the 
<a href="http://www.townhall.com/townhall/townhall_shop/welcome.html.cgi">Town 
Hall store</a>
